chiron (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Operating doctrine (generalized) with completion contract and
    pre-response check, plus compressed per-turn reminder.
  * Claude Code adapter: session-start ground-truth hook with canary,
    per-turn reminder hook, PreToolUse guard (denies --no-verify,
    error swallowing, force pushes, test deletion/weakening), Stop
    verification gate. All fail-soft.
  * Codex CLI adapter: AGENTS.md template plus doctrine install.
  * chiron install/doctor CLI with live hook self-test.
  * A/B eval harness with pre-registered mechanical checks, canary
    validity gating, positive control, and claim-disciplined report.

